Package: physmerge
Title: Physical Locus Merging for GWAS Summary Statistics
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Pin", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "your@email.com")
Description: Collapses overlapping genomic signals into non-overlapping locus
    blocks using a forward sliding-window approach, without requiring an LD
    reference panel. Supports p-values and test statistics, REML-GPCM
    per-SNP output, and standard PLINK2 summary statistics.
